            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>No. GBP requires a real physical location or service-area business. City pages exist to rank in organic results for cities where you don't have a physical GBP presence — they are complementary, not a replacement.</p></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>

